To those people who are getting error (0xE8008001)

Hi, are you tired of getting error, surprised while installing your favorite app in your i-device? Worry no more, here is the sweet solution.

Use your i-device to download any free or paid (if you don't care about those ninety nine cents) app or game from iTunes store and install in your i-device (iPhone, iPod etc). 

Next try installing your beloved app or game which annoyed you with error (0xE8008001)

Works like magic. See, the DRM (a protocol that validates genuine apps) of your device needs a confirmation that if you are an iTune customer and when it sees the cracked apps without genuine pass will be included in an error table, only ANY valid install from iTunes will drop that table to blank.

Hope this helps.
